{"type":"message","id":"c11b4810","parentId":"9e51e76e","timestamp":"2026-04-10T16:48:03.607Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool_hm9uqolaK1kLkBQ6rPVB708V","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nproject_id: \"PROJ-20260325-001\"\nname: \"ECC Second Brain Framework\"\nstatus: \"active\"\npriority: \"high\"\nstartDate: \"2026-03-25\"\ndueDate: \"2026-03-26\"\ncompletion: 95\ntags:\n  - project\n  - ecc\n  - framework\n---\n\n# ECC Second Brain Framework\n\n## Overview\n\n| Property | Value |\n|----------|-------|\n| **Project ID** | `PROJ-20260325-001` |\n| **Status** | 🟢 Active |\n| **Priority** | 🔴 High |\n| **Start Date** | 2026-03-25 |\n| **Due Date** | 2026-03-26 |\n| **Completion** | 95% |\n\n---\n\n## Goal\n\nImplementiere ein vollständiges ECC-Second-Brain-Framework mit Obsidian-Integration basierend auf dem aktuellen OpenClaw-Stand.\n\n---\n\n## Success Criteria\n\n- [x] ECC-CORE mit Error-Handler und Logging\n- [x] Obsidian-Integration mit Plugin\n- [x] Second-Brain-Struktur (PARA)\n- [x] Sync-Skript für OpenClaw\n- [x] Stabilitätsmechanismen\n- [x] Setup-README und Dokumentation\n\n---\n\n## Architecture\n\n```mermaid\ngraph TB\n    subgraph OpenClaw\n        A[Registry] --> B[Sessions]\n        A --> C[Commands]\n        A --> D[Agents]\n    end\n    \n    subgraph Sync\n        B --> E[Sync Script]\n        E --> F[YAML Parser]\n        E --> G[Mermaid Gen]\n        E --> H[Code Extract]\n    end\n    \n    subgraph Obsidian\n        F --> I[Daily Notes]\n        G --> J[Diagrams]\n        H --> K[Snippets]\n        I --> L[Dataview]\n    end\n```\n\n---\n\n## Components\n\n### 1. ECC-CORE\n- Error-Handler mit Try-Catch\n- Winston-Logger mit Datei-Rotation\n- Eval-Runner mit CI-Template\n- Backup/Restore-Kommandos\n- Retry-Logik\n\n### 2. Obsidian-Integration\n- manifest.json mit ID \"ecc-second-brain\"\n- data.json für Plugin-Einstellungen\n- styles.css für ECC-Theme\n- Daily-Notes-Template\n- Tag-System\n\n### 3. Second-Brain-Struktur\n- 00-Inbox/ (neue Inputs)\n- 01-Projects/ (aktive Projekte)\n- 02-Areas/ (langfristige Bereiche)\n- 03-Resources/ (Skills, Patterns, Snippets)\n- 04-Archive/ (abgeschlossene Sessions)\n- 05-Daily/ (tägliche Session-Logs)\n\n### 4. Sync-Skript\n- OpenClaw → Obsidian Sync\n- Mermaid-Diagramme\n- Code-Block-Extraktion\n- Dataview-Queries\n- Backlinks\n\n### 5. Stabilität\n- Drift-Detection\n- Auto-Backup\n- Context-Switches\n- API-Key-Verschlüsselung\n\n---\n\n## Decisions #decision\n\n### ADR-001: YAML vs JSON\n**Decision:** YAML für Registry (menschenlesbar), JSON für Indizes (Performance)\n**Rationale:** Best of both worlds\n\n### ADR-002: File-based vs Database\n**Decision:** Keine SQLite, file-basierte Registry\n**Rationale:** Konsistent mit OpenClaw's Memory-System\n\n---\n\n## Notes\n\nFramework basiert auf dem OpenClaw-Stand vom 2026-03-25.\n\n---\n\n*ECC Second Brain Framework Project*\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775839683597}}
{"type":"message","id":"73fc6c20","parentId":"c11b4810","timestamp":"2026-04-10T16:48:03.617Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool_o5OsB1bjAODrjszUOG8fKtvg","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\ndate: 2026-03-26\ntime: \"00:24\"\nsession_id: \"20260326002400\"\nagent: andrew-main\ntype: session\nsource: memory/2026-03-26.md\ntags: [framework, implementation, ecc-integration, complete]\nrelated_sessions: []\ndecisions: [ADR-001, ADR-002, ADR-003, ADR-004, ADR-005]\nprojects: [PROJ-001]\n---\n\n# Session 2026-03-26: Framework Completion\n\n## Zusammenfassung\nKomplette Implementierung des Modular Agent Frameworks mit ECC-Integration.\n90+ Dateien erstellt, 27/27 Validierungen bestanden.\n\n> 🔄 *Migriert aus altem SecondBrain (2026-04-09)*\n\n## Getroffene Entscheidungen\n- [x] [[../../01-Projects/proj-ecc-framework#ADR-001|ADR-001: YAML vs JSON]] - Architektur-Entscheidung\n- [x] [[../../01-Projects/proj-ecc-framework#ADR-002|ADR-002: File-based vs Database]] - Speicher-Strategie\n- [x] [[../../01-Projects/proj-ecc-framework#ADR-003|ADR-003: SKILL.md Format]] - Skill-Standard\n- [x] [[../../01-Projects/proj-ecc-framework#ADR-004|ADR-004: Hybrid Error Handling]] - Fehlerbehandlung\n- [x] [[../../01-Projects/proj-ecc-framework#ADR-005|ADR-005: MCP Integration Prep]] - Erweiterbarkeit\n\n## Erstellte Komponenten\n- ✅ 4 Phasen (Registry, Cognitive, Persistence, Operations)\n- ✅ 6 Spezialisierte Agenten\n- ✅ 11 Skills\n- ✅ 22 Commands\n- ✅ 3 Contexts (dev, research, review)\n- ✅ GitHub Actions (3 Workflows)\n- ✅ MCP Configs (6 Server)\n- ✅ Second Brain (PARA-System)\n\n## Statistiken\n| Metrik | Wert |\n|--------|------|\n| **Dateien** | 90+ |\n| **Validierung** | 27/27 (100%) |\n| **Version** | 1.3.0 |\n| **Status** | Production Ready |\n\n## Verknüpfungen\n- 🔗 **Projekt:** [[../../01-Projects/proj-ecc-framework|ECC Framework Implementation]]\n- 🔗 **Dashboard:** [[../../00-Dashboard/Dashboard|Dashboard]]\n- 🔗 **Extern:** [Session Summary](../../../../../../../../Documents/Andrew%20Openclaw/session-summary)\n\n## Tags\n#framework #implementation #ecc-integration #complete #migrated"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775839683606}}
{"type":"message","id":"39dbbaf9","parentId":"73fc6c20","timestamp":"2026-04-10T16:48:03.624Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool_oqlQT3kmQEznZvUsgosICIAR","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\ntags:\n  - index\n  - moc\n  - startseite\n---\n\n# ECC Second Brain 🧠\n\n> **Master Map of Content** - Dein zentrales Navigations-Dashboard\n\n---\n\n## Quick Links\n\n| Bereich | Beschreibung | Link |\n|---------|--------------|------|\n| **Inbox** | Neue Inputs & Quick Capture | [[00-Inbox/README\\|Inbox]] |\n| **Projekte** | Aktive ECC-Projekte | [[01-Projects/README\\|Projekte]] |\n| **Bereiche** | Langfristige Verantwortung | [[02-Areas/README\\|Bereiche]] |\n| **Ressourcen** | Wiederverwendbares Wissen | [[03-Resources/README\\|Ressourcen]] |\n| **Archiv** | Abgeschlossene Sessions | [[04-Archive/README\\|Archiv]] |\n| **Daily** | Tägliche Session-Logs | [[05-Daily/README\\|Daily]] |\n\n---\n\n## Aktive Projekte\n\n```dataview\nTABLE status, startDate, dueDate, completion\nFROM \"01-Projects\"\nWHERE status = \"active\"\nSORT priority DESC, startDate DESC\n```\n\n---\n\n## Offene TODOs\n\n```dataview\nTASK\nFROM #todo\nWHERE !completed\nSORT priority DESC, dueDate ASC\nLIMIT 10\n```\n\n---\n\n## Letzte Entscheidungen\n\n```dataview\nTABLE decision_id, status, date\nFROM #decision\nWHERE status = \"accepted\"\nSORT date DESC\nLIMIT 5\n```\n\n---\n\n## Session-Statistiken\n\n```dataview\nTABLE date, tokens_used, agent_mode\nFROM \"05-Daily\"\nSORT date DESC\nLIMIT 7\n```\n\n---\n\n## Tags\n\n### System-Tags\n- `#decision` - Architekturentscheidungen\n- `#todo` - Offene Aufgaben\n- `#insight` - Erkenntnisse\n- `#session` - Session-Logs\n- `#context` - Kontext-Informationen\n- `#project` - Projekte\n- `#area` - Bereiche\n\n### Tag-Cloud\n\n```dataview\nTABLE length(rows) as Count\nFLATTEN file.tags as Tag\nFROM \"\"\nWHERE !contains([\"#decision\", \"#todo\", \"#insight\", \"#session\", \"#context\", \"#project\", \"#area\"], Tag)\nGROUP BY Tag\nWHERE length(rows) >= 2\nSORT length(rows) DESC\nLIMIT 20\n```\n\n---\n\n## Wöchentliche Übersicht\n\n| Tag | Sessions | Tokens | Entscheidungen |\n|-----|----------|--------|----------------|\n| Montag | | | |\n| Dienstag | | | |\n| Mittwoch | | | |\n| Donnerstag | | | |\n| Freitag | | | |\n\n---\n\n## Sync-Status\n\n- **Letzter Sync**: \n- **Sync-Quelle**: OpenClaw\n- **Vault-Version**: 1.0.0\n\n---\n\n*ECC Second Brain Framework v1.0.0*\n*Powered by Obsidian + OpenClaw*\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775839683618}}
