{"type":"message","id":"5835f86b","parentId":"4b24c396","timestamp":"2026-04-10T18:47:53.333Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool_mEmlHj7RM0xci6W0kTGM2Wy5","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\ndate: 10-04-2026\ntype: moc\ncategory: navigation\ntags: [moc, dashboard, startseite, navigation]\n---\n\n# 🏠 Second Brain - Startseite\n\n> **Master Map of Content** - Dein zentrales Navigations-Dashboard\n\n---\n\n## 📊 Übersichten\n\n| Bereich | Beschreibung | Link |\n|---------|--------------|------|\n| **Daily** | Tagesnotizen & Sessions | [[01-Daily/_MOC-Daily\\|Daily Übersicht]] |\n| **Projekte** | Aktive & abgeschlossene Projekte | [[02-Projects/_MOC-Projects\\|Projekt-Übersicht]] |\n| **Wissen** | How-To's, Konzepte, Referenzen | [[03-Knowledge/_MOC-Knowledge\\|Wissens-Übersicht]] |\n| **Entscheidungen** | Architektur-Entscheidungen (ADRs) | [[04-Decisions/\\|Entscheidungen]] |\n| **Meine Fähigkeiten** | Was ich alles kann | [[00-Meta/Capabilities-Index\\|💡 Meine Tools & Skills]] |\n\n---\n\n## 🔥 Aktive Projekte\n\n```dataview\nTABLE status, priority, completion as \"%\"\nFROM \"02-Projects\"\nWHERE status = \"active\"\nSORT priority DESC, startDate DESC\n```\n\n---\n\n## 📝 Letzte Sessions\n\n```dataview\nTABLE date, type, tags\nFROM \"01-Daily\"\nSORT date DESC\nLIMIT 10\n```\n\n---\n\n## ✅ Offene TODOs\n\n```dataview\nTASK\nFROM #todo\nWHERE !completed\nSORT priority DESC, dueDate ASC\nLIMIT 15\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🏷️ Wichtige Tags\n\n### System-Tags\n- `#decision` - Architekturentscheidungen\n- `#todo` - Offene Aufgaben\n- `#insight` - Erkenntnisse & Learnings\n- `#session` - Session-Logs\n- `#project` - Projekte\n- `#how-to` - Anleitungen\n\n### Themen-Tags\n```dataview\nTABLE length(rows) as \"Anzahl\"\nFLATTEN file.tags as Tag\nFROM \"\"\nWHERE !contains([\"#decision\", \"#todo\", \"#insight\", \"#session\", \"#project\", \"#how-to\", \"#moc\", \"#reference\", \"#knowledge\", \"#daily\"], Tag)\nGROUP BY Tag\nWHERE length(rows) >= 2\nSORT length(rows) DESC\nLIMIT 15\n```\n\n---\n\n## 📅 Letzte Entscheidungen\n\n```dataview\nTABLE decision_id, status, date\nFROM \"04-Decisions\"\nWHERE status = \"accepted\"\nSORT date DESC\nLIMIT 5\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🛠️ Schnellzugriff: Meine Fähigkeiten\n\n> **Neu:** Alle meine Skills, Tools und Commands auf einen Blick  \n> → [[00-Meta/Capabilities-Index|💡 Hier klicken für die komplette Übersicht]]\n\n**Beliebt:**\n- [[00-Meta/Capabilities-Index#Security Review|🔒 Security Review]] - Code auf Schwachstellen prüfen\n- [[00-Meta/Capabilities-Index#Grill Me|🔥 Grill Me]] - Deinen Plan auf Schwächen testen\n- [[00-Meta/Capabilities-Index#Plan Feature|📋 Plan Feature]] - Feature in Schritte zerlegen\n- [[00-Meta/Capabilities-Index#TDD Loop|🧪 TDD Loop]] - Test-driven Development\n\n---\n\n## 🔗 Externe Links\n\n| Ressource | Link |\n|-----------|------|\n| **OpenClaw Docs** | `~/.openclaw/workspace/docs/` |\n| **Skills Ordner** | `~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/` |\n| **Memory (Sessions)** | `~/.openclaw/workspace/memory/` |\n| **Outside Resources** | `~/Documents/Outside_resources/` |\n\n---\n\n## 📈 Statistiken\n\n```dataview\nTABLE WITHOUT ID\n  length(filter(file.inlinks, (f) => contains(f.path, \"01-Daily\"))) as \"Daily Notes\",\n  length(filter(file.inlinks, (f) => contains(f.path, \"02-Projects\"))) as \"Projekte\",\n  length(filter(file.inlinks, (f) => contains(f.path, \"03-Knowledge\"))) as \"Wissen\",\n  length(filter(file.inlinks, (f) => contains(f.path, \"04-Decisions\"))) as \"Entscheidungen\"\nFROM \"\"\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🔄 Sync-Status\n\n- **Letzter Sync:** `=this.date`\n- **Vault-Version:** 2.0\n- **Struktur:** PARA + Second Brain Hybrid\n\n---\n\n*Powered by Obsidian + OpenClaw + ECC Framework*  \n*Letzte Aktualisierung: 10-04-2026*\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775846873327}}
{"type":"message","id":"96f4b34f","parentId":"5835f86b","timestamp":"2026-04-10T18:48:01.131Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Jetzt muss ich:\n1. Backup erstellen\n2. DataviewJS-Queries hinzufügen\n3. Die Startseite erweitern\n\nIch muss vorsichtig sein mit den DataviewJS-Queries - die müssen funktionieren.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Backup erstellen und DataviewJS-Queries hinzufügen..."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_R2tw78qKt0y5jgxvzUzPjLin","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Backup _MOC-Startseite.md\n$backupPath = \"C:\\Users\\andre\\.openclaw\\workspace\\SecondBrain\\00-Meta\\Backups\\20260410-203552\"\nCopy-Item -Path \"C:\\Users\\andre\\.openclaw\\workspace\\SecondBrain\\_MOC-Startseite.md\" -Destination \"$backupPath\\_MOC-Startseite.md.backup\" -Force\nWrite-Host \"Startseite backup erstellt\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":174098,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":174098,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775846873339}}
