{"type":"message","id":"58fe2741","parentId":"a6fc7d02","timestamp":"2026-04-10T18:59:09.017Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Gute Frage! Ich sollte prüfen, was wir aktuell haben. Laut MEMORY.md haben wir:\n\n- `sync-openclaw-to-obsidian.ps1` - Sync zwischen OpenClaw und Vault\n- `auto-backup.ps1` - Automatische Backups\n\nAber das sind PowerShell-Scripts, kein Obsidian-Plugin.\n\nDas ECC-Vault Plugin wäre ein echtes Obsidian-Plugin mit:\n- Automatischem Sync (alle 30 Minuten)\n- Integration in die Obsidian UI\n- Echtzeit-Updates\n\nDas ist etwas anderes als unsere PowerShell-Scripts.\n\nIch sollte das klären.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Ausgezeichnete Frage! Lass mich prüfen, was wir aktuell haben:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_QK4eVLf429dQDgxh60ZXLj3T","name":"memory_search","arguments":{"query":"automatisch synchronisieren sync openclaw obsidian"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":153424,"output":197,"cacheRead":23808,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":177429,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775847482354}}
