{"type":"message","id":"d4ddb14a","parentId":"0b69683d","timestamp":"2026-04-10T19:38:51.889Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Ich soll die relevanten Teile aus den Areas und Dataview-Queries übernehmen. Das sind konkrete, nützliche Erweiterungen:\n\n1. Areas-Konzept (Development, Research) - als neue Ordner/Struktur\n2. Nützliche Dataview-Queries zu unserem Dashboard hinzufügen\n\nIch werde das systematisch machen mit Backup und Tests.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Verstanden! Übernehme Areas + Dataview-Queries systematisch:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_SFbTEKP6IBzFtHTXpqN9FeQT","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Backup erstellen\n$date = Get-Date -Format \"yyyyMMdd-HHmmss\"\n$backupPath = \"C:\\Users\\andre\\.openclaw\\workspace\\SecondBrain\\00-Meta\\Backups\\$date\"\nNew-Item -ItemType Directory -Path $backupPath -Force\nCopy-Item -Path \"C:\\Users\\andre\\.openclaw\\workspace\\SecondBrain\\_MOC-Startseite.md\" -Destination $backupPath -Force\nWrite-Host \"Backup erstellt: $backupPath\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_FwnRl21EOIiUwigDa30ABxal","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Areas-Ordner erstellen\nNew-Item -ItemType Directory -Path \"C:\\Users\\andre\\.openclaw\\workspace\\SecondBrain\\02-Areas\" -Force\nWrite-Host \"Areas-Ordner erstellt\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":83134,"output":302,"cacheRead":98048,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":181484,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775849882814}}
