{"type":"message","id":"9b0ced15","parentId":"f10b5dcd","timestamp":"2026-04-10T19:41:27.602Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Jetzt sollte ich eine Zusammenfassung aller Änderungen geben.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"## ✅ ÜBERNAHME ABGESCHLOSSEN!\n\n### Was wurde übernommen:\n\n#### A) Areas (Verantwortungsbereiche)\n| Datei | Zweck |\n|-------|-------|\n| `02-Areas/area-development.md` | Technische Entwicklung (weekly review) |\n| `02-Areas/area-research.md` | Wissensaufbau (monthly review) |\n| `02-Areas/README.md` | Dokumentation des Areas-Konzepts |\n\n**Neue Struktur:** PARA + Projects + Areas + Knowledge\n\n#### B) Dataview-Queries\n| Query | Zweck |\n|-------|-------|\n| Token Usage pro Monat | Monatliche Statistiken |\n| Überfällige TODOs | Due Date < today |\n| Sessions nach Token-Usage | Top-Verbraucher |\n| Areas-Review | Welche Areas brauchen Review? |\n| Wochenübersicht | Tasks pro Tag |\n| Tag-Cloud | Top 20 Tags |\n\n**Dokumentiert in:** `03-Knowledge/References/erweiterte-dataview-queries.md`\n\n---\n\n### Tests durchführen..."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_hFHBdlo5LlKUoryjJqRxZU13","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Test 1: Areas existieren?\n$test1 = Test-Path \"C:\\Users\\andre\\.openclaw\\workspace\\SecondBrain\\02-Areas\\area-development.md\"\nWrite-Host \"Test 1 - Development Area: $test1\"\n\n# Test 2: Research Area existiert?\n$test2 = Test-Path \"C:\\Users\\andre\\.openclaw\\workspace\\SecondBrain\\02-Areas\\area-research.md\"\nWrite-Host \"Test 2 - Research Area: $test2\"\n\n# Test 3: Areas README existiert?\n$test3 = Test-Path \"C:\\Users\\andre\\.openclaw\\workspace\\SecondBrain\\02-Areas\\README.md\"\nWrite-Host \"Test 3 - Areas README: $test3\"\n\n# Test 4: Dataview-Queries Dokument existiert?\n$test4 = Test-Path \"C:\\Users\\andre\\.openclaw\\workspace\\SecondBrain\\03-Knowledge\\References\\erweiterte-dataview-queries.md\"\nWrite-Host \"Test 4 - Dataview Queries: $test4\"\n\n# Test 5: Backup existiert?\n$test5 = Test-Path \"C:\\Users\\andre\\.openclaw\\workspace\\SecondBrain\\00-Meta\\Backups\\20260410-213852\"\nWrite-Host \"Test 5 - Backup: $test5\"\n\nWrite-Host \"\"\nWrite-Host \"=== ERGEBNIS ===\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\nif ($test1 -and $test2 -and $test3 -and $test4 -and $test5) {\n    Write-Host \"ALLE TESTS BESTANDEN\" -ForegroundColor Green\n} else {\n    Write-Host \"FEHLER\" -ForegroundColor Red\n}","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":178007,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":178007,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775850063787}}
{"type":"message","id":"bcc9b719","parentId":"9b0ced15","timestamp":"2026-04-10T19:41:28.077Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool_hFHBdlo5LlKUoryjJqRxZU13","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Test 1 - Development Area: True\nTest 2 - Research Area: True\nTest 3 - Areas README: True\nTest 4 - Dataview Queries: True\nTest 5 - Backup: True\n\n=== ERGEBNIS ===\nALLE TESTS BESTANDEN"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":460,"aggregated":"Test 1 - Development Area: True\nTest 2 - Research Area: True\nTest 3 - Areas README: True\nTest 4 - Dataview Queries: True\nTest 5 - Backup: True\n\n=== ERGEBNIS ===\nALLE TESTS BESTANDEN","cwd":"C:\\Users\\andre\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775850088073}}
{"type":"message","id":"4220e408","parentId":"bcc9b719","timestamp":"2026-04-10T19:41:38.461Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Perfekt! Alle Tests bestanden. Jetzt sollte ich eine abschließende Zusammenfassung geben.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"🎉 **ALLE TESTS BESTANDEN!**\n\n## ✅ ÜBERNAHME AUS ECC-FRAMEWORK KOMPLETT\n\n### Übernommen:\n\n| Bereich | Dateien | Status |\n|---------|---------|--------|\n| **Areas** | 3 | ✅ Development, Research, README |\n| **Dataview-Queries** | 6 neue Queries | ✅ Dokumentiert |\n| **Backups** | 1 | ✅ Vorhanden |\n\n### Neue Vault-Struktur:\n```\nSecondBrain/\n├── 00-Meta/\n├── 01-Daily/\n├── 02-Projects/\n├── **02-Areas/** ← NEU\n│   ├── area-development.md\n│   ├── area-research.md\n│   └── README.md\n├── 03-Knowledge/\n│   └── References/\n│       └── erweiterte-dataview-queries.md ← NEU\n├── 04-Decisions/\n└── ...\n```\n\n### Was jetzt möglich ist:\n1. **Areas pflegen** mit weekly/monthly reviews\n2. **Erweiterte Dashboard-Queries** nutzen\n3. **Langfristige Verantwortung** tracken (neben Projekten)\n\n---\n\n**Soll ich jetzt weitermachen mit:**\n- Anderen Archiv-Ordnern (Prompt Execution, Master Rework)?\n- Oder ist Schluss für heute?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":178759,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":178759,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775850088084}}
