{"type":"message","id":"fbbf26ce","parentId":"37bc2091","timestamp":"2026-04-10T20:03:17.065Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Der Nutzer will, dass ich ALLE verbleibenden 27 Dateien analysiere und bewerte, ob sie für unser OpenClaw Harness nützlich sind. Ich muss systematisch vorgehen und alle Dateitypen berücksichtigen, nicht nur .md.\n\nIch werde die Analyse in Kategorien durchführen:\n1. .obsidian/ Configs\n2. config/ YAML-Dateien\n3. scripts/ PowerShell\n4. lib/ PowerShell Module\n5. Sonstiges (package.json, Setup)\n\nUnd dann für jede entscheiden: Übernehmen / Ignorieren / Archivieren.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Verstanden! Systematische Analyse ALLER 27 verbleibenden Dateien nach Kategorien:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_Y5mNie1kGFLh4g3jmysiBQf2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Analyse nach Kategorien\nWrite-Host \"=== SYSTEMATISCHE ANALYSE: ALLE 27 FEHLENDEN DATEIEN ===\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\nWrite-Host \"\"\n\n$basePath = \"C:\\Users\\andre\\.openclaw\\workspace\\vault-archive\\Main_Obsidian_Vault\\Kimi_Agent_ECC-Second-Brain-Framework Implementiert\\SecondBrain\"\n\n# Kategorie 1: .obsidian Configs\nWrite-Host \"1. OBSIDIAN CONFIGS (Plugin-Einstellungen)\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n$obsidianFiles = @(\n    \".obsidian\\app.json\",\n    \".obsidian\\appearance.json\", \n    \".obsidian\\core-plugins.json\",\n    \".obsidian\\plugins\\ecc-vault\\data.json\",\n    \".obsidian\\plugins\\ecc-vault\\manifest.json\",\n    \".obsidian\\plugins\\ecc-vault\\README.md\",\n    \".obsidian\\plugins\\ecc-vault\\secure-keys.json\",\n    \".obsidian\\plugins\\ecc-vault\\styles.css\",\n    \".obsidian\\snippets\\ecc-second-brain.css\",\n    \".obsidian\\templates\\daily-note-template.md\",\n    \".obsidian\\templates\\decision-template.md\"\n)\n\nforeach ($file in $obsidianFiles) {\n    $fullPath = Join-Path $basePath $file\n    $exists = Test-Path $fullPath\n    $size = if ($exists) { (Get-Item $fullPath).Length } else { 0 }\n    Write-Host \"   $file`: $size bytes\" -ForegroundColor $(if($exists){\"Green\"}else{\"Red\"})\n}\n\nWrite-Host \"\"\nWrite-Host \"   Bewertung: Plugin-spezifisch, NICHT fuer OpenClaw Harness relevant\" -ForegroundColor Gray\nWrite-Host \"   -> IGNORIEREN (nur fuer reines Obsidian-Plugin)\" -ForegroundColor Gray\n\nWrite-Host \"\"\n\n# Kategorie 2: Configs\nWrite-Host \"2. CONFIG (YAML-Konfigurationen)\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n$configFiles = @(\n    \"config\\drift-config.yaml\",\n    \"config\\eval-template.yaml\",\n    \"config\\stability-config.yaml\"\n)\n\nforeach ($file in $configFiles) {\n    $fullPath = Join-Path $basePath $file\n    $exists = Test-Path $fullPath\n    Write-Host \"   $file`: $(if($exists){'VORHANDEN'}else{'FEHLT'})\" -ForegroundColor $(if($exists){\"Green\"}else{\"Red\"})\n}\n\nWrite-Host \"\"\nWrite-Host \"   Bewertung: Koennten nuetzliche Default-Konfigurationen enthalten\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\nWrite-Host \"   -> ANALYSIEREN\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n\nWrite-Host \"\"\n\n# Kategorie 3: Scripts\nWrite-Host \"3. SCRIPTS (PowerShell)\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n$scriptFiles = @(\n    \"scripts\\auto-backup.ps1\",\n    \"scripts\\cmd-backup.ps1\",\n    \"scripts\\context-switch.ps1\",\n    \"scripts\\drift-detection.ps1\",\n    \"scripts\\eval-runner.ps1\",\n    \"scripts\\sync-openclaw-to-obsidian.ps1\",\n    \"Setup-SecondBrain.ps1\"\n)\n\nforeach ($file in $scriptFiles) {\n    $fullPath = Join-Path $basePath $file\n    $exists = Test-Path $fullPath\n    $size = if ($exists) { (Get-Item $fullPath).Length } else { 0 }\n    Write-Host \"   $file`: $size bytes\" -ForegroundColor $(if($exists){\"Green\"}else{\"Red\"})\n}\n\nWrite-Host \"\"\nWrite-Host \"   Bewertung: Koennten Verbesserungen zu unseren Scripts enthalten\" -ForegroundColor Red\nWrite-Host \"   -> ANALYSIEREN (HOHE PRIORITAET)\" -ForegroundColor Red\n\nWrite-Host \"\"\n\n# Kategorie 4: Lib Module\nWrite-Host \"4. LIB MODULE (PowerShell Module)\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n$libFiles = @(\n    \"scripts\\lib\\DataviewQuery.psm1\",\n    \"scripts\\lib\\Encryption.psm1\",\n    \"scripts\\lib\\ErrorHandler.psm1\",\n    \"scripts\\lib\\Logging.psm1\",\n    \"scripts\\lib\\MermaidGenerator.psm1\"\n)\n\nforeach ($file in $libFiles) {\n    $fullPath = Join-Path $basePath $file\n    $exists = Test-Path $fullPath\n    $size = if ($exists) { (Get-Item $fullPath).Length } else { 0 }\n    Write-Host \"   $file`: $size bytes\" -ForegroundColor $(if($exists){\"Green\"}else{\"Red\"})\n}\n\nWrite-Host \"\"\nWrite-Host \"   Bewertung: Vergleichen mit unseren existierenden Modulen\" -ForegroundColor Red\nWrite-Host \"   -> ANALYSIEREN (HOHE PRIORITAET)\" -ForegroundColor Red\n\nWrite-Host \"\"\n\n# Kategorie 5: Sonstiges\nWrite-Host \"5. SONSTIGES\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\nWrite-Host \"   package.json: Node.js Konfiguration\" -ForegroundColor Gray\nWrite-Host \"   -> IGNORIEREN (nur fuer Node-Entwicklung)\" -ForegroundColor Gray\n\nWrite-Host \"\"\nWrite-Host \"=== EMPFEHLUNG ===\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\nWrite-Host \"PRIORITAET 1 (Analysieren): Scripts + Lib Module (12 Dateien)\" -ForegroundColor Red\nWrite-Host \"PRIORITAET 2 (Analysieren): Config YAMLs (3 Dateien)\" -ForegroundColor Yellow  \nWrite-Host \"IGNORIEREN: Obsidian-Configs + package.json (12 Dateien)\" -ForegroundColor Gray","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":191997,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":191997,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775851357611}}
