{"type":"message","id":"74f67af6","parentId":"dbda7553","timestamp":"2026-04-10T20:03:34.502Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Gute Übersicht! Jetzt muss ich die wichtigen Dateien lesen und bewerten. Ich fange mit Priorität 1 an: Scripts und Lib Module.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Jetzt die wichtigen Dateien analysieren - beginne mit Priorität 1:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_Pn1V9xb60MVkwdd9OVx7J1gr","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\andre\\.openclaw\\workspace\\vault-archive\\Main_Obsidian_Vault\\Kimi_Agent_ECC-Second-Brain-Framework Implementiert\\SecondBrain\\scripts\\sync-openclaw-to-obsidian.ps1","limit":50}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_NDMdf6viHamb9ih6Sd61WMVH","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\andre\\.openclaw\\workspace\\vault-archive\\Main_Obsidian_Vault\\Kimi_Agent_ECC-Second-Brain-Framework Implementiert\\SecondBrain\\scripts\\lib\\Encryption.psm1","limit":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_1dyIi5Q95YTRMiB8xGudqwYb","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\andre\\.openclaw\\workspace\\vault-archive\\Main_Obsidian_Vault\\Kimi_Agent_ECC-Second-Brain-Framework Implementiert\\SecondBrain\\config\\drift-config.yaml"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":189131,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":189131,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775851397658}}
{"type":"message","id":"0a2a3715","parentId":"74f67af6","timestamp":"2026-04-10T20:03:34.531Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool_Pn1V9xb60MVkwdd9OVx7J1gr","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#Requires -Version 5.1\n<#\n.SYNOPSIS\n    Sync-Skript für OpenClaw → Obsidian Integration\n\n.DESCRIPTION\n    Synchronisiert OpenClaw-Sessions mit dem ECC Second Brain Obsidian Vault.\n    Generiert Daily Notes, Mermaid-Diagramme, Code-Blocks und Backlinks.\n\n.PARAMETER SessionId\n    Spezifische Session-ID zum Syncen\n\n.PARAMETER VaultPath\n    Pfad zum Obsidian Vault\n\n.PARAMETER DryRun\n    Zeigt an, was synchronisiert würde, ohne Änderungen vorzunehmen\n\n.PARAMETER Force\n    Überschreibt existierende Dateien\n\n.EXAMPLE\n    .\\sync-openclaw-to-obsidian.ps1\n    .\\sync-openclaw-to-obsidian.ps1 -SessionId \"sess_abc123\" -DryRun\n\n.NOTES\n    Author: Andrew (andrew-main)\n    Version: 1.0.0\n    ECC Framework: Sync Integration\n#>\n\n[CmdletBinding()]\nparam(\n    [Parameter(Mandatory = $false)]\n    [string]$SessionId = $null,\n    \n    [Parameter(Mandatory = $false)]\n    [string]$VaultPath = \"C:\\Users\\andre\\Documents\\Andrew Openclaw\\SecondBrain\",\n    \n    [Parameter(Mandatory = $false)]\n    [switch]$DryRun,\n    \n    [Parameter(Mandatory = $false)]\n    [switch]$Force\n)\n\n# Script Variables\n$script:Version = \"1.0.0\"\n$script:StartTime = Get-Date\n$script:LogFile = Join-Path $VaultPath \".logs\" \"sync-$(Get-Date -Format 'yyyyMMdd-HHmmss').log\"\n\n[408 more lines in file. Use offset=51 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775851414526}}
{"type":"message","id":"45717ff4","parentId":"0a2a3715","timestamp":"2026-04-10T20:03:34.535Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool_NDMdf6viHamb9ih6Sd61WMVH","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#Requires -Version 5.1\n<#\n.SYNOPSIS\n    ECC Encryption Module - AES-256-GCM Verschlüsselung für API-Keys\n\n.DESCRIPTION\n    Sicheres Verschlüsselungsmodul für das ECC Second Brain Framework.\n    Verwendet AES-256-GCM für API-Keys und sensible Daten.\n\n.EXAMPLE\n    Protect-ApiKey -KeyName \"OpenAI\" -ApiKey \"sk-...\"\n    Unprotect-ApiKey -KeyName \"OpenAI\"\n\n.NOTES\n    Author: Andrew (andrew-main)\n    Version: 1.0.0\n    ECC Framework: Security\n#>\n\n# Module Variables\n$script:ModuleVersion = \"1.0.0\"\n$script:KeyStoragePath = Join-Path $PSScriptRoot \"..\\..\\.obsidian\\plugins\\ecc-vault\\secure-keys.json\"\n$script:MasterKeyPath = Join-Path $PSScriptRoot \"..\\..\\.obsidian\\plugins\\ecc-vault\\.masterkey\"\n\n#region Public Functions\n\n<#\n.SYNOPSIS\n    Verschlüsselt einen API-Key\n\n\n[379 more lines in file. Use offset=31 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775851414531}}
{"type":"message","id":"a1b7952f","parentId":"45717ff4","timestamp":"2026-04-10T20:03:34.541Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool_1dyIi5Q95YTRMiB8xGudqwYb","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# ECC Second Brain - Drift Detection Configuration\n# Referenz-Struktur für Vault-Validierung\n\nversion: \"1.0.0\"\ndescription: \"Reference structure for ECC Second Brain Vault\"\n\n# Tolerance Settings\ntolerance:\n  # Allow additional files not in reference\n  allow_extra_files: true\n  \n  # Allow missing optional files\n  allow_missing_optional: true\n  \n  # Maximum drift percentage before warning\n  max_drift_percent: 10\n\n# Required Folders (must exist)\nrequired_folders:\n  - path: \"00-Inbox\"\n    description: \"Quick capture zone for new inputs\"\n    optional: false\n  \n  - path: \"01-Projects\"\n    description: \"Active ECC projects\"\n    optional: false\n  \n  - path: \"02-Areas\"\n    description: \"Long-term areas of responsibility\"\n    optional: false\n  \n  - path: \"03-Resources\"\n    description: \"Reusable knowledge and resources\"\n    optional: false\n  \n  - path: \"03-Resources/Skills\"\n    description: \"Skills and competencies\"\n    optional: false\n  \n  - path: \"03-Resources/Patterns\"\n    description: \"Code patterns and best practices\"\n    optional: false\n  \n  - path: \"03-Resources/Snippets\"\n    description: \"Code snippets\"\n    optional: false\n  \n  - path: \"04-Archive\"\n    description: \"Completed sessions\"\n    optional: false\n  \n  - path: \"05-Daily\"\n    description: \"Daily session logs\"\n    optional: false\n  \n  - path: \"scripts\"\n    description: \"Automation scripts\"\n    optional: false\n  \n  - path: \"scripts/lib\"\n    description: \"PowerShell modules\"\n    optional: false\n  \n  - path: \"config\"\n    description: \"Configuration files\"\n    optional: false\n  \n  - path: \".logs\"\n    description: \"Log files\"\n    optional: true\n  \n  - path: \".backups\"\n    description: \"Backup files\"\n    optional: true\n  \n  - path: \".obsidian\"\n    description: \"Obsidian configuration\"\n    optional: false\n  \n  - path: \".obsidian/plugins/ecc-vault\"\n    description: \"ECC Vault plugin\"\n    optional: false\n  \n  - path: \".obsidian/snippets\"\n    description: \"CSS snippets\"\n    optional: true\n  \n  - path: \".obsidian/templates\"\n    description: \"Note templates\"\n    optional: false\n\n# Required Files (must exist)\nrequired_files:\n  - path: \"README.md\"\n    description: \"Main documentation\"\n    optional: false\n  \n  - path: \"Setup-SecondBrain.ps1\"\n    description: \"Setup script\"\n    optional: false\n  \n  - path: \"scripts/lib/ErrorHandler.psm1\"\n    description: \"Error handling module\"\n    optional: false\n  \n  - path: \"scripts/lib/Logging.psm1\"\n    description: \"Logging module\"\n    optional: false\n  \n  - path: \"scripts/lib/MermaidGenerator.psm1\"\n    description: \"Mermaid diagram generator\"\n    optional: false\n  \n  - path: \"scripts/lib/DataviewQuery.psm1\"\n    description: \"Dataview query generator\"\n    optional: false\n  \n  - path: \"scripts/lib/Encryption.psm1\"\n    description: \"Encryption module\"\n    optional: false\n  \n  - path: \"scripts/sync-openclaw-to-obsidian.ps1\"\n    description: \"Sync script\"\n    optional: false\n  \n  - path: \".obsidian/plugins/ecc-vault/manifest.json\"\n    description: \"Plugin manifest\"\n    optional: false\n  \n  - path: \".obsidian/plugins/ecc-vault/data.json\"\n    description: \"Plugin configuration\"\n    optional: false\n  \n  - path: \".obsidian/plugins/ecc-vault/styles.css\"\n    description: \"Plugin styles\"\n    optional: false\n  \n  - path: \".obsidian/templates/daily-note-template.md\"\n    description: \"Daily note template\"\n    optional: false\n  \n  - path: \".obsidian/templates/decision-template.md\"\n    description: \"Decision template\"\n    optional: false\n\n# File Patterns (must match at least one)\nrequired_patterns:\n  - pattern: \"00-Inbox/*.md\"\n    description: \"Inbox notes\"\n    min_count: 0\n    optional: true\n  \n  - pattern: \"01-Projects/*.md\"\n    description: \"Project notes\"\n    min_count: 0\n    optional: true\n  \n  - pattern: \"05-Daily/*.md\"\n    description: \"Daily notes\"\n    min_count: 0\n    optional: true\n\n# Auto-Fix Settings\nauto_fix:\n  enabled: true\n  actions:\n    - create_missing_folders\n    - create_missing_templates\n    - fix_permissions\n  \n  exclude:\n    - \".obsidian/workspace.json\"\n    - \".obsidian/graph.json\"\n    - \".logs/*\"\n    - \".backups/*\"\n\n# Reporting\nreport:\n  format: \"markdown\"\n  output: \".logs/drift-report.md\"\n  include_recommendations: true\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775851414536}}
